Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is supposed to be a labyrinth.\NWhy's there a bed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue! Wake up, Yue!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the hell up already,\Nyou sexy blood-sucking space cadet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:00:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's me, sleepyhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Looks like I had you worried to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maverick's lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happened after all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door opened, and we found this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I put you on the bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like the Holy Water\Nwas starting to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I had used my powers to their limits...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all the help. I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were dirty, so I helped clean you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you licking your lips?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that laugh for?!\NWhat'd you do to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And stop licking your lips!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you find all these clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the Maverick a guy, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found more than just clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like we've gotta\Nstart searching the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you after there, Yue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing fits me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun? No, it couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At nighttime, it turns into the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty big house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked around a bit and found\Na lot of rooms I couldn't get into.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay alert, all right, Yue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an actual bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, how many months has\Nit been since I've taken a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to get in together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather take a long one by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The library and workshop on the\Nsecond floor are both sealed off, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see the third floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this is the only room up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like he was waiting for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room's gotta be the key\Nto finding a route to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Transmute ability wouldn't\Neven work on those sealed rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue, help me out if this goes south.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Oscar Orcus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the man who built this labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done well to survive\Nmy trials and make it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The term "Maverick"\Nshould be familiar to you, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but you'll have to hold off on questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a recording, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I can't answer your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to leave a message\Nfor the person who made it here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to share the reasons why someone who knew\Nthe truth of this world chose to fight against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the 65th floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're down to the\Ndeepest floor anyone's made it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. I was worried how\Nthings would turn out at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but everyone's gotten so strong.\NI was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk--you've\Nleveled up quite a bit, Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as much as Mister Hero, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This map only shows part of this level.\NWe've no idea what will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That monster again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it died!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behemoth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows the respawn rate\Nof monsters here in the labyrinth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it is normal for some monsters\Nto respawn after being defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes! Don't forget\Nto secure an escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meld-{\i1}san{\i0}, we're not\Nthe same as we were before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're hundreds of times stronger!\NWe won't lose again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to win this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Doesn't feel right\Nfor us to keep up this losing streak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for a rematch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you take another one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to press past you\Nand keep moving forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soar to the heavens with\Nthe speed of a thousand wings--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavenly Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku, take the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyama and the others, go behind it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meld-{\i1}san{\i0}, take the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rear guard, prepare the\Nmagic circle, a high-level one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct, unwavering orders--excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the raging power to rend the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Herculean Strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crumble to ash, to splinters, to dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overpower!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still tough as ever, isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let this supreme strike slice through all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obliterate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let this gentle light envelop you--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentle Halo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luminous Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O heavenly blessing, lend them your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Recovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can still do that,\Neven with his horns broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, get ready to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:12:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemies of God mayst\Nnot tread upon His holy ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Herem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blessing of heaven,\Nreveal your secrets--Divine Strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kaorin! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blazing Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Limit Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did we beat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Victory is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, Shizuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}! It's nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about\Nhow we've finally made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are or why you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's something I want you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use it as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just please don't use it for evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all. Thank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you will be able\Nto live by your own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like something's being\Nimprinted onto my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't evil gods,\Nor Mavericks, they were Liberators...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, I don't give a crap\Nabout what happens to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worried about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, also it seems like I've learned\Na new kind of magic--ancient magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called "creation magic."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It lets me add energy to raw minerals\Nto give them special qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make artifacts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's incredible, Hajime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna learn how to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:16:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't use Transmute...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure, but it's ancient magic, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No harm in learning how to use it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so, Hajime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going? Learn how yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but artifacts are hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That so? Guess ancient magic's more\Ncompatible with some casters than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, this place is ours now,\Nso why don't we take care of his corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use it to fertilize the fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo! Found it, Yue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like that magic circle\Nis connected to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to connect it, we need Orcus' ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:17:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I grabbed it when we buried him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the workshop's full of\NOscar's artifacts and all his materials, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better take 'em with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is that how it works, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I make it through the other labyrinths,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get my hands on the\Nother forms of ancient magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might find a way to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Guess that's what we gotta do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hit up those other labyrinths!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are even more in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:18:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yue, let's stay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get up to the surface, but there\Nare too many things to learn down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we're going to go\Nthrough the other labyrinths,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should prepare as much as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, as long as I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, little miss Yue, I think I told you\NI was gonna bathe alone, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least cover your chest!\NThere were tons of towels!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, Yue, look, I'm--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not your type?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not it! You're totally my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of me is yours, Hajime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's touching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, your--\NNope! I'm getting out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're fully prepared.\NI've learned all I can from monster meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all geared up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took us a whole two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:21:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue, my weapons and powers\Naren't normal up on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Holy Church and other kingdoms\Nwon't be able to keep quiet about 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be fine if it were just them, but we\Nmight even get targeted by godly beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might just be us against\Nthe world on this journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may not have enough lives\Nsaved up to survive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you, and you'll protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're gonna defeat\Neverything and everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and surpass the entire world, together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:05.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Good morning," "Good night,"\Nall those simple things
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:10.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,are so dreamlike and beloved to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.24,0:22:14.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I finally met you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:21.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is so special, thank you again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:29.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd be lonely all by myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:34.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, until you found me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:40.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:45.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, until I thought of a world without you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:52.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe it?\NI miss you, I'm so fond of you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:58.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, don't forget it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:03.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine bright like the first star in the night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:09.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and stay closer to me than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:14.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:20.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let go of that hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:27.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay by my side and shine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ARIFURETA: From Commonplace\Nto World's Strongest